# 🎵 Spotify Web Music Player Clone

A sleek and responsive clone of the Spotify web music player interface, built entirely with HTML and CSS. This project recreates the visual experience of Spotify’s desktop player, showcasing modern UI design and layout techniques.

## 🚀 Features

- 🎧 Clean and minimal Spotify-inspired layout  
- 📱 Responsive design for desktop and mobile views  
- 🎨 Styled using pure CSS (no frameworks)  
- 🖼️ Includes sidebar, main player area, and footer controls  
- 🔍 Hover effects and transitions for interactive feel

## 📂 Project Structure
## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5  
- CSS3 (Flexbox, Grid, Transitions)
